text: $NFLX should sell a large convertible... now
It's been three weeks in which I vowed not to tweet about @realDonaldTrump - and while no one should give a crap about that decision... I feel relieved.
The comparison between bitcoin at $20,000 a few months ago and the S&P Index at 2815 today is unfair. But there is a grain of truth somewhere in that comparison!

That sort of hubris is half of the reason that The Oracle of Omaha wrote: "Be greedy when others are fearful and fearful when others are greedy." It has served him well. It will serve all of us well to consider.

Talking heads display self confidence and hubris - often at tops. The sharper the advance, the more audible the view. History is dotted with this frequent occurrence. Unfortunately the only certainty is the lack of certainty.
